1 A SENATE RESOLUTION CONFIRMING TEENA PICCIONE AS THE STATE CHIEF
2 INFORMATION OFFICER AND SECRETARY OF THE DEPARTMENT OF
3 INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY.
4 Be it resolved by the Senate:
5 SECTION 1. Having given due consideration to the matter, the Senate confirms
6 Teena Piccione as the State Chief Information Officer and Secretary of the Department of
7 Information Technology.
8 SECTION 2. This resolution is effective upon adoption.
